  "title": "Shipping Executive #79682",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Manufacturing/Food Production</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Shipping Executive</strong></li><li>Working Location: Jurong West</li><li>Working Hours: 5 days, Mon - Fri (8am – 5.00pm)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Up to $3000 + Variable Bonus + $90 (Transport Allowance)</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Possess thorough knowledge of shipping processes including import and export documentation such as Bill of Lading (B/L), health certificates, certificates of origin, Free Trade Agreements (FTA), and vessel bookings.</li><li>Capable of independently managing and executing all shipping duties.</li><li>Coordinate with production and warehouse departments to ensure products are ready for shipment.</li><li>Organize container bookings and oversee the loading process.</li><li>Prepare and distribute all required shipping documents to customers efficiently.</li><li>Other ad-hoc duties which may be assigned.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum GCE ‘O’ Level and or min 2 years of relevant experience.</li><li>Proficient in MS Office.</li><li>Knowledge of various shipping document and FTA Certificate application.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#79682 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
